c: 5
v: 75
t: "Akayilutho uMesiya (uJesu) indodana kaMariya ngaphandle kokuthi wayeyisithunywa (sikaMvelinqangi) izithunywa sezadlula ngaphambilini kwakhe futhi unina wakhe wayengowesifazane oneqiniso, bobabili babekudla ukudla, bheka ukuthi sibacacisela kanjani izimpawu bese ubheka ukuthi baduka kanjani"